[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.346,
    "endTime": 18.36,
    "text": "About 75 years ago,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.36,
    "endTime": 20.595,
    "text": "my grandfather, a young man,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.595,
    "endTime": 22.506,
    "text": "walked into a tent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.506,
    "endTime": 24.3,
    "text": "that was converted into a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.3,
    "endTime": 25.714000000000002,
    "text": "movie theater like that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.714,
    "endTime": 27.912999999999997,
    "text": "and he fell hopelessly in love"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.914,
    "endTime": 29.243000000000002,
    "text": "with the woman he saw on the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.243,
    "endTime": 32.571,
    "text": "silver screen: none other than Mae West,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.572,
    "endTime": 34.487,
    "text": "the heartthrob of the '30s,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.487,
    "endTime": 36.527,
    "text": "and he could never forget her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.527,
    "endTime": 38.447,
    "text": "In fact, when he had his daughter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.447,
    "endTime": 40.639,
    "text": "many years later, he wanted to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.639,
    "endTime": 42.550000000000004,
    "text": "name her after Mae West,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.55,
    "endTime": 43.638999999999996,
    "text": "but can you imagine an Indian"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.639,
    "endTime": 45.175000000000004,
    "text": "child name Mae West?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.175,
    "endTime": 46.861,
    "text": "The Indian family said, no way!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.861,
    "endTime": 49.799,
    "text": "So when my twin brother Kaesava"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.799,
    "endTime": 52.309,
    "text": "was born, he decided to tinker"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.309,
    "endTime": 54.239999999999995,
    "text": "with the spelling of Keshava's name."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.24,
    "endTime": 57.735,
    "text": "He said, if Mae West can be M-A-E,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.735,
    "endTime": 61.271,
    "text": "why can't Keshava be K-A-E?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.271,
    "endTime": 63.511,
    "text": "So he changed Kaesava's spelling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.511,
    "endTime": 65.58200000000001,
    "text": "Now Kaesava had a baby boy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.582,
    "endTime": 67.782,
    "text": "called Rehan a couple of weeks ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.782,
    "endTime": 70.11999999999999,
    "text": "He decided to spell, or, rather,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.13,
    "endTime": 72.92999999999999,
    "text": "misspell Raehan with an A-E."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.93,
    "endTime": 74.22800000000001,
    "text": "You know, my grandfather died"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.228,
    "endTime": 75.588,
    "text": "many years ago when I was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.588,
    "endTime": 77.428,
    "text": "little, but his love for Mae"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.429,
    "endTime": 79.9,
    "text": "West lives on as a misspelling"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.9,
    "endTime": 81.676,
    "text": "in the DNA of his progeny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.676,
    "endTime": 84.82000000000001,
    "text": "That for me is successful legacy. (Laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.82,
    "endTime": 86.461,
    "text": "You know, as for me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.462,
    "endTime": 87.68900000000001,
    "text": "my wife and I have our own"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.689,
    "endTime": 89.297,
    "text": "crazy legacy project."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.297,
    "endTime": 91.489,
    "text": "We actually sit every few years,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.489,
    "endTime": 93.86200000000001,
    "text": "argue, disagree, fight,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.862,
    "endTime": 95.704,
    "text": "and actually come up with our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.704,
    "endTime": 97.72,
    "text": "very own 200-year plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.72,
    "endTime": 99.679,
    "text": "Our friends think we're mad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.68,
    "endTime": 101.168,
    "text": "Our parents think we're cuckoo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.168,
    "endTime": 102.504,
    "text": "Because, you know, we both"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.504,
    "endTime": 103.872,
    "text": "come from families that really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.872,
    "endTime": 106.873,
    "text": "look up to humility and wisdom,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.873,
    "endTime": 108.504,
    "text": "but we both like to live"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.504,
    "endTime": 109.84100000000001,
    "text": "larger than life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.841,
    "endTime": 111.351,
    "text": "I believe in the concept of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.351,
    "endTime": 114.112,
    "text": "a Raja Yogi: Be a dude before"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.112,
    "endTime": 115.425,
    "text": "you can become an ascetic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.425,
    "endTime": 116.92,
    "text": "This is me being a rock star,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.92,
    "endTime": 118.544,
    "text": "even if it's in my own house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.544,
    "endTime": 119.80799999999999,
    "text": "You know?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.808,
    "endTime": 121.52000000000001,
    "text": "So when Netra and I sat down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.52,
    "endTime": 122.976,
    "text": "to make our first plan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.976,
    "endTime": 124.96,
    "text": "10 years ago, we said"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.96,
    "endTime": 127.64,
    "text": "we want the focus of this plan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.64,
    "endTime": 128.88,
    "text": "to go way beyond ourselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.88,
    "endTime": 131.543,
    "text": "What do we mean by beyond ourselves?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.544,
    "endTime": 134.56900000000002,
    "text": "Well 200 years, we calculated,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.569,
    "endTime": 136.744,
    "text": "is at the end of our direct"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.744,
    "endTime": 137.912,
    "text": "contact with the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.912,
    "endTime": 139.27100000000002,
    "text": "There's nobody I'll meet in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.271,
    "endTime": 141.583,
    "text": "my life will ever live beyond"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.584,
    "endTime": 143.488,
    "text": "200 years, so we thought"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.488,
    "endTime": 144.68,
    "text": "that's a perfect place where"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.68,
    "endTime": 146.592,
    "text": "we should situate our plan and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.592,
    "endTime": 148.32000000000002,
    "text": "let our imagination take flight."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.32,
    "endTime": 149.864,
    "text": "You know, I never really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.864,
    "endTime": 151.552,
    "text": "believed in legacy. What am I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.552,
    "endTime": 153.543,
    "text": "going to leave behind? I'm an artist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.544,
    "endTime": 156.83,
    "text": "Until I made a cartoon about 9/11."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.83,
    "endTime": 159.478,
    "text": "It caused so much trouble for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.478,
    "endTime": 160.894,
    "text": "I was so upset."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.894,
    "endTime": 163.374,
    "text": "You know, a cartoon that was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.374,
    "endTime": 165.37,
    "text": "meant to be a cartoon of the week"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.38,
    "endTime": 168.26999999999998,
    "text": "ended up staying so much longer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.27,
    "endTime": 170.424,
    "text": "Now I'm in the business of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.424,
    "endTime": 172.101,
    "text": "creating art that will"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.101,
    "endTime": 174.464,
    "text": "definitely even outlive me, and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.464,
    "endTime": 176.125,
    "text": "I think about what I want to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.125,
    "endTime": 178.165,
    "text": "leave behind through those paintings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.165,
    "endTime": 180.156,
    "text": "You know, the 9/11 cartoon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.157,
    "endTime": 183.453,
    "text": "upset me so much that I decided"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.453,
    "endTime": 184.989,
    "text": "I'll never cartoon again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.989,
    "endTime": 186.205,
    "text": "I said, I'm never going to make any"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.205,
    "endTime": 188.11800000000002,
    "text": "honest public commentary again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.118,
    "endTime": 190.613,
    "text": "But of course I continued"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.613,
    "endTime": 192.549,
    "text": "creating artwork that was honest"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.549,
    "endTime": 194.726,
    "text": "and raw, because I forgot about"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.726,
    "endTime": 196.944,
    "text": "how people reacted to my work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.944,
    "endTime": 198.518,
    "text": "You know, sometimes forgetting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.518,
    "endTime": 201.50900000000001,
    "text": "is so important to remain idealistic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.509,
    "endTime": 204.24499999999998,
    "text": "Perhaps loss of memory is so"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.246,
    "endTime": 206.18900000000002,
    "text": "crucial for our survival"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.189,
    "endTime": 207.558,
    "text": "as human beings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.558,
    "endTime": 209.412,
    "text": "One of the most important things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.413,
    "endTime": 211.317,
    "text": "in my 200-year plan that Netra"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.317,
    "endTime": 213.703,
    "text": "and I write is what to forget"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.703,
    "endTime": 215.16,
    "text": "about ourselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.16,
    "endTime": 216.436,
    "text": "You know, we carry so much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.437,
    "endTime": 217.846,
    "text": "baggage, from our parents,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.846,
    "endTime": 219.854,
    "text": "from our society, from so many"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.854,
    "endTime": 223.598,
    "text": "people -- fears, insecurities -- and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.598,
    "endTime": 225.453,
    "text": "our 200-year plan really lists"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.453,
    "endTime": 228.505,
    "text": "all our childhood problems that we have to expire."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.505,
    "endTime": 230.6,
    "text": "We actually put an expiry date"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.6,
    "endTime": 232.48,
    "text": "on all our childhood problems."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.48,
    "endTime": 234.345,
    "text": "The latest date I put was,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.345,
    "endTime": 237.106,
    "text": "I said, I am going to expire"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.106,
    "endTime": 239.649,
    "text": "my fear of my leftist, feminist"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.649,
    "endTime": 242.58,
    "text": "mother-in-law, and this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.58,
    "endTime": 245.18,
    "text": "today is the date! (Laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.18,
    "endTime": 246.77100000000002,
    "text": "She's watching. (Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.771,
    "endTime": 251.619,
    "text": "Anyway, you know, I really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.619,
    "endTime": 253.619,
    "text": "make decisions all the time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.619,
    "endTime": 255.204,
    "text": "about how I want to remember"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.204,
    "endTime": 258.476,
    "text": "myself, and that's the most important"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.476,
    "endTime": 259.995,
    "text": "kind of decisions I make."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.995,
    "endTime": 261.867,
    "text": "And this directly translates"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.867,
    "endTime": 263.19,
    "text": "into my paintings."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.19,
    "endTime": 265.332,
    "text": "But like my friends, I can do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.332,
    "endTime": 266.908,
    "text": "that really well on Facebook,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.908,
    "endTime": 268.827,
    "text": "Pinterest, Twitter, Flickr, YouTube."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.827,
    "endTime": 270.26,
    "text": "Name it, I'm on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.26,
    "endTime": 272.339,
    "text": "I've started outsourcing my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.339,
    "endTime": 273.932,
    "text": "memory to the digital world,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.932,
    "endTime": 275.372,
    "text": "you know? But that comes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.372,
    "endTime": 276.468,
    "text": "with a problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.468,
    "endTime": 278.99,
    "text": "It's so easy to think of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.99,
    "endTime": 279.404,
    "text": "technology as a metaphor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.404,
    "endTime": 281.75,
    "text": "for memory, but our brains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.75,
    "endTime": 283.697,
    "text": "are not perfect storage devices"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.697,
    "endTime": 284.496,
    "text": "like technology."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.496,
    "endTime": 286.35999999999996,
    "text": "We only remember what we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.36,
    "endTime": 287.291,
    "text": "want to. At least I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.291,
    "endTime": 289.794,
    "text": "And I rather think of our brains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.794,
    "endTime": 292.193,
    "text": "as biased curators of our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.193,
    "endTime": 295.32,
    "text": "memory, you know? And if"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.33,
    "endTime": 296.85699999999997,
    "text": "technology is not a metaphor for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.857,
    "endTime": 298.48900000000003,
    "text": "memory, what is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.489,
    "endTime": 301.505,
    "text": "Netra and I use our technology"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.505,
    "endTime": 304.73,
    "text": "as a tool in our 200-year plan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.73,
    "endTime": 307.59200000000004,
    "text": "to really curate our digital legacy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.592,
    "endTime": 310.609,
    "text": "That is a picture of my mother,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.609,
    "endTime": 313.361,
    "text": "and she recently got a Facebook account."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.362,
    "endTime": 315.12800000000004,
    "text": "You know where this is going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.128,
    "endTime": 316.962,
    "text": "And I've been very supportive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.962,
    "endTime": 319.344,
    "text": "until this picture shows up"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.345,
    "endTime": 320.91200000000003,
    "text": "on my Facebook page. (Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.912,
    "endTime": 324.169,
    "text": "And I actually untagged myself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.169,
    "endTime": 325.633,
    "text": "first, then I picked up the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.633,
    "endTime": 326.991,
    "text": "phone. I said, \"Mom, you will"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.992,
    "endTime": 328.10400000000004,
    "text": "never put a picture of me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.104,
    "endTime": 329.393,
    "text": "in a bikini ever again.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.393,
    "endTime": 332.32,
    "text": "And she said, \"Why? You look"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.321,
    "endTime": 334.44000000000005,
    "text": "so cute, darling.\" I said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.44,
    "endTime": 336.233,
    "text": "\"You just don't understand.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.233,
    "endTime": 338.216,
    "text": "Maybe we are among the first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.216,
    "endTime": 339.53700000000003,
    "text": "generation that really understands"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.537,
    "endTime": 341.727,
    "text": "this digital curating of ourselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.728,
    "endTime": 343.29,
    "text": "Maybe we are the first to even"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.29,
    "endTime": 345.528,
    "text": "actively record our lives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.528,
    "endTime": 347.8,
    "text": "You know, whether you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.8,
    "endTime": 349.233,
    "text": "agree with, you know, legacy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.233,
    "endTime": 351.376,
    "text": "or not, we are actually leaving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.376,
    "endTime": 353.729,
    "text": "behind digital traces all the time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.729,
    "endTime": 355.784,
    "text": "So Netra and I really wanted"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.784,
    "endTime": 357.144,
    "text": "to use our 200-year plan"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.144,
    "endTime": 359.321,
    "text": "to curate this digital legacy,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.321,
    "endTime": 361.16,
    "text": "and not only digital legacy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.16,
    "endTime": 362.32000000000005,
    "text": "but we believe in curating"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.32,
    "endTime": 364.207,
    "text": "the legacy of my past"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.208,
    "endTime": 365.39200000000005,
    "text": "and future."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.392,
    "endTime": 367.225,
    "text": "How, you may ask?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.225,
    "endTime": 370.793,
    "text": "Well, when I think of the future,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.793,
    "endTime": 372.985,
    "text": "I never see myself moving forward"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.985,
    "endTime": 375.17,
    "text": "in time. I actually see time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.17,
    "endTime": 377.89000000000004,
    "text": "moving backward towards me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.89,
    "endTime": 378.489,
    "text": "I can actually visualize"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.489,
    "endTime": 379.84,
    "text": "my future approaching."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.84,
    "endTime": 381.953,
    "text": "I can dodge what I don't want"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.953,
    "endTime": 383.441,
    "text": "and pull in what I want."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.441,
    "endTime": 384.751,
    "text": "It's like a video game obstacle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.752,
    "endTime": 387.238,
    "text": "course. And I've gotten better and better"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.238,
    "endTime": 389.71,
    "text": "at doing this. Even when I make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.71,
    "endTime": 391.104,
    "text": "a painting, I actually imagine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.104,
    "endTime": 393.135,
    "text": "I'm behind the painting,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.135,
    "endTime": 394.318,
    "text": "it already exists, and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394.318,
    "endTime": 395.534,
    "text": "someone's looking at it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.534,
    "endTime": 396.623,
    "text": "and I see whether they're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.624,
    "endTime": 398.245,
    "text": "feeling it from their gut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.245,
    "endTime": 399.478,
    "text": "Are they feeling it from their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.478,
    "endTime": 402.144,
    "text": "heart, or is it just a cerebral thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.144,
    "endTime": 404.252,
    "text": "And it really informs my painting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.252,
    "endTime": 405.443,
    "text": "Even when I do an art show,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.443,
    "endTime": 406.467,
    "text": "I really think about, what should"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.467,
    "endTime": 408.19,
    "text": "people walk away with?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.19,
    "endTime": 410.955,
    "text": "I remember when I was 19,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.955,
    "endTime": 413.91999999999996,
    "text": "I did, I wanted to do my first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.92,
    "endTime": 416.29200000000003,
    "text": "art exhibition, and I wanted the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.292,
    "endTime": 417.698,
    "text": "whole world to know about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.699,
    "endTime": 419.147,
    "text": "I didn't know TED then,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.147,
    "endTime": 421.147,
    "text": "but what I did was I closed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.148,
    "endTime": 422.916,
    "text": "my eyes tight, and I started"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.916,
    "endTime": 425.188,
    "text": "dreaming. I could imagine people"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.188,
    "endTime": 426.731,
    "text": "coming in, dressed up, looking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.731,
    "endTime": 428.764,
    "text": "beautiful, my paintings with all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 428.764,
    "endTime": 431.475,
    "text": "the light, and in my visualization"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.475,
    "endTime": 433.331,
    "text": "I actually saw a very famous"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 433.331,
    "endTime": 435.499,
    "text": "actress launching my show,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.499,
    "endTime": 436.99600000000004,
    "text": "giving credibility to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.996,
    "endTime": 439.58,
    "text": "And I woke up from my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.59,
    "endTime": 440.316,
    "text": "visualization and I said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.316,
    "endTime": 442.51,
    "text": "who was that? I couldn't tell"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.52,
    "endTime": 444.291,
    "text": "if it was Shabana Azmi or Rekha,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.291,
    "endTime": 446.5,
    "text": "two very famous Indian actresses,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.5,
    "endTime": 448.347,
    "text": "like the Meryl Streeps of India."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.347,
    "endTime": 450.707,
    "text": "As it turned out, next morning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 450.707,
    "endTime": 452.427,
    "text": "I wrote a letter to both of them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452.427,
    "endTime": 454.38,
    "text": "and Shabana Azmi replied,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.38,
    "endTime": 456.147,
    "text": "and came and launched"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.147,
    "endTime": 459.212,
    "text": "my very first show 12 years ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.212,
    "endTime": 461.444,
    "text": "And what a bang it started"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.444,
    "endTime": 463.244,
    "text": "my career with! You know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.244,
    "endTime": 465.66,
    "text": "when we think of time in this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.66,
    "endTime": 467.97900000000004,
    "text": "way, we can curate not only the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.979,
    "endTime": 471.496,
    "text": "future but also the past."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471.496,
    "endTime": 473.7,
    "text": "This is a picture of my family,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 473.7,
    "endTime": 476.323,
    "text": "and that is Netra, my wife."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.323,
    "endTime": 477.955,
    "text": "She's the co-creator of my"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 477.955,
    "endTime": 479.436,
    "text": "200-year plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.436,
    "endTime": 481.474,
    "text": "Netra's a high school history"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 481.475,
    "endTime": 483.41900000000004,
    "text": "teacher. I love Netra,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.419,
    "endTime": 485.236,
    "text": "but I hate history."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 485.236,
    "endTime": 487.147,
    "text": "I keep saying, \"Nets, you live"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.148,
    "endTime": 488.795,
    "text": "in the past while I'll create"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 488.795,
    "endTime": 490.796,
    "text": "the future, and when I'm done,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.796,
    "endTime": 492.292,
    "text": "you can study about it.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.292,
    "endTime": 494.251,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 494.252,
    "endTime": 496.25100000000003,
    "text": "She gave me an indulgent smile,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 496.251,
    "endTime": 498.388,
    "text": "and as punishment, she said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 498.388,
    "endTime": 500.123,
    "text": "\"Tomorrow I'm teaching a class"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.123,
    "endTime": 502.284,
    "text": "on Indian history, and you are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.284,
    "endTime": 503.73199999999997,
    "text": "sitting in it, and I'm grading you.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.732,
    "endTime": 506.75,
    "text": "I'm like, \"Oh, God.\" I went."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 506.75,
    "endTime": 507.378,
    "text": "I actually went and sat in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.379,
    "endTime": 509.572,
    "text": "on her class. She started by"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.572,
    "endTime": 511.867,
    "text": "giving students primary source"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 511.867,
    "endTime": 514.482,
    "text": "documents from India, Pakistan,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514.482,
    "endTime": 516.731,
    "text": "from Britain, and I said,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.731,
    "endTime": 518.875,
    "text": "\"Wow.\" Then she asked them to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 518.875,
    "endTime": 520.827,
    "text": "separate fact from bias."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.827,
    "endTime": 523.619,
    "text": "I said, \"Wow,\" again."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523.619,
    "endTime": 526.5790000000001,
    "text": "Then she said, \"Choose your"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.579,
    "endTime": 529.882,
    "text": "facts and biases and create an"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.883,
    "endTime": 532.162,
    "text": "image of your own story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.162,
    "endTime": 533.571,
    "text": "of dignity.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.571,
    "endTime": 536.826,
    "text": "History as an imaging tool?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 536.826,
    "endTime": 538.4590000000001,
    "text": "I was so inspired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 538.459,
    "endTime": 539.819,
    "text": "I went and created my own"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.819,
    "endTime": 541.396,
    "text": "version of Indian history."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.396,
    "endTime": 543.2819999999999,
    "text": "I actually included stories from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 543.283,
    "endTime": 544.3050000000001,
    "text": "my grandmother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.305,
    "endTime": 545.4639999999999,
    "text": "She used to work for the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.464,
    "endTime": 547.32,
    "text": "telephone exchange, and she used"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 547.32,
    "endTime": 548.1590000000001,
    "text": "to actually overhear conversations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.159,
    "endTime": 550.328,
    "text": "between Nehru and Edwina Mountbatten."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 550.328,
    "endTime": 551.904,
    "text": "And she used to hear all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.904,
    "endTime": 553.39,
    "text": "kinds of things she shouldn't"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.39,
    "endTime": 555.545,
    "text": "have heard. But, you know,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.545,
    "endTime": 556.711,
    "text": "I include things like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.711,
    "endTime": 559.505,
    "text": "This is my version of Indian history."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559.505,
    "endTime": 563.79,
    "text": "You know, if this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 563.791,
    "endTime": 565.9050000000001,
    "text": "is so, it occurred to me that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 565.905,
    "endTime": 568.127,
    "text": "maybe, just maybe, the primary"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.128,
    "endTime": 569.567,
    "text": "objective of our brains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.567,
    "endTime": 572.607,
    "text": "is to serve our dignity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 572.607,
    "endTime": 574.615,
    "text": "Go tell Facebook to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.615,
    "endTime": 575.924,
    "text": "figure that out!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 575.924,
    "endTime": 578.544,
    "text": "Netra and I don't write our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.544,
    "endTime": 580.357,
    "text": "200-year plan for someone else"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.357,
    "endTime": 581.381,
    "text": "to come and execute it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.381,
    "endTime": 583.524,
    "text": "in 150 years. Imagine receiving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.524,
    "endTime": 585.421,
    "text": "a parcel saying, from the past,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.421,
    "endTime": 586.7840000000001,
    "text": "okay now you're supposed to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 586.784,
    "endTime": 587.749,
    "text": "spend the rest of your life"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.749,
    "endTime": 589.207,
    "text": "doing all of this. No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.207,
    "endTime": 590.854,
    "text": "We actually write it only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.854,
    "endTime": 593.344,
    "text": "to set our attitudes right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.344,
    "endTime": 597.1840000000001,
    "text": "You know, I used to believe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.184,
    "endTime": 598.584,
    "text": "that education is the most"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 598.584,
    "endTime": 600.64,
    "text": "important tool to leave"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.65,
    "endTime": 601.5219999999999,
    "text": "a meaningful legacy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.522,
    "endTime": 603.46,
    "text": "Education is great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 603.46,
    "endTime": 604.695,
    "text": "It really teaches us who"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.695,
    "endTime": 606.3100000000001,
    "text": "we are, and helps us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.31,
    "endTime": 607.3489999999999,
    "text": "contextualize ourselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 607.35,
    "endTime": 609.316,
    "text": "in the world, but it's really"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.316,
    "endTime": 611.375,
    "text": "my creativity that's taught me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 611.375,
    "endTime": 613.152,
    "text": "that I can be much more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.152,
    "endTime": 615.3430000000001,
    "text": "than what my education told me I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.343,
    "endTime": 616.7959999999999,
    "text": "I'd like to make"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 616.797,
    "endTime": 619.1270000000001,
    "text": "the argument that creativity is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.127,
    "endTime": 621.558,
    "text": "the most important tool we have."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.558,
    "endTime": 623.744,
    "text": "It lets us create who we are,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.744,
    "endTime": 625.655,
    "text": "and curate what is to come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.655,
    "endTime": 628.895,
    "text": "I like to think -- Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 628.895,
    "endTime": 630.47,
    "text": "I like to think of myself"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.47,
    "endTime": 632.806,
    "text": "as a storyteller, where my past"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.806,
    "endTime": 635.87,
    "text": "and my future are only stories,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 635.87,
    "endTime": 638.159,
    "text": "my stories, waiting to be told"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 638.159,
    "endTime": 640.774,
    "text": "and retold. I hope all of you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 640.774,
    "endTime": 642.718,
    "text": "one day get a chance to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.718,
    "endTime": 644.545,
    "text": "share and write your own"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.545,
    "endTime": 645.91,
    "text": "200-year story."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 645.91,
    "endTime": 646.975,
    "text": "Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.975,
    "endTime": 649.158,
    "text": "Shukran! (Applause)"
  }
]